'''''Mwami''''' ni izina ryicyubahiro  mu bice by'[[Afurika]] y'iburasirazuba ndetse niyo hagati. Iri zina risobanura ''umutware'' mubwoko bwindimi zitwa bantu. Iri zina kandi ryakoreshejwe mu mateka n'abami mu bihugu byinshi bya [[Afurika]], kandi n'ubu riracyakoreshwa ku bami gakondo cyangwa abategetsi b'uturere mu bihugu byinshi byo muri [[Afurika]].

== Umutware w'ubwoko ==
Mu ndimi nyinshi zo muri aka gace, harimo [[Ikirundi]],[[Ikinyarwanda]],nizindi- ijambo  ''mwami'' rivuze"Umutware w'ubwoko". Iri rero rikoreshwa nk'inyito ku mutware wese muri izi nce.

Byongeye ho, ''mwami'' bisobanura "umutware" cyangwa " umugabo " mu rurimi rw'ikigande . Ikoreshwa nk'izina ry'umuyobozi mukuru mu batware bavuga ururimi rw'ikigande hirya no hino mu [[Ibiyaga Bigari|karere k'ibiyaga bigari bya Afurika]], nubwo ishobora no gukoreshwa nk'icyubahiro rusange ku bagabo, kimwe n'icyongereza ''Bwana''

Abatware gakondo ba Lenje nabanya Ila bo muri [[Zambiya]], hamwe nabanya Tonga bo muri [[Zambiya]] na [[Zimbabwe]] nabo bakoresha icyubahiro.

== Umwami ==
Mu Bwami bw'u [[Rwanda]], [[Urutonde rw'Abami bayoboye u Rwanda|Umwami w'u Rwanda]] yari azwi ku izina rya ''mwami'' ( ''abami mwu bwinshi'' ). Kuva mu 1961, igihugu cyayobowe na [[Perezida wa Repubulika y’u Rwanda|perezida w'u Rwanda]] .

Ubwami bw'[[Uburundi]] bwategekwaga n'abami ''bitwaga mwami'', hagakurikiraho rimwe mu mazina ane ya regnal yakurikiyeho. Perezida w'[[Uburundi]] yategetse kuva repubulika yatangira mu 1966.

Uhereye mu mwaka wa 2020, ikitwa ubwami bwa Buha, mu gace ka Kigoma mu burengerazuba ha [[Tanzaniya]] buyobowe n'Umwami uturuka Manyavu,witwa Elifas Robert.

Ubwami gakondo mu [[Intara ya Kivu y’Amajyaruguru|ntara ya Kivu y'Amajyaruguru]], [[Intara ya Kivu y’Amajyaruguru|Kivu]] [[Intara ya Kivu y’Amajyepfo|y'Amajyepfo]], na Maniema muri [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo]] bita abayobozi babo gakondo ''mwami'' .

Abanya Luhya bo mu burengerazuba bwa [[Kenya]] bavuga ko umutegetsi wabo w'ikirenga ari ''Mwami'' .
